name: Optimus Inu
description: Optimus is a humanoid robot, created by Tesla. Optimus Inu is your chance to get in early with this huge narrative. If you understand Elon Musk’s influence on memecoins, then you can get an idea of how much attention we will get with Elon talking about his robot. A token was made out of Elon Musk’s dog(Floki) which had an all time high mcap of $3.5bl. Now we have Elon Musk’s robot. The potential upside is incredible, and we cant wait to go on this journey with all of you.
